<p>This uses <code>UserEditForm</code>, so go open that as well.</p>
<p>In <code>buildForm()</code>, we'll do the <em>exact</em> same thing we did on the genus form: add
a new field called <code>studiedGenuses</code> - that's the property name on <code>User</code> that we
want to modify:</p>
