<p>Keep going: use <code>EntityType::class</code> and then set the options: <code>class</code> set now to
<code>Genus::class</code> to make <code>Genus</code> checkboxes. Then, <code>multiple</code> set to <code>true</code>, <code>expanded</code>
set to <code>true</code>, and <code>choice_label</code> set to <code>name</code> to display that field from <code>Genus</code>:</p>
